_sText: This is a map I started a few years ago. It was initially for minigame for CSS. I decided to finish it and make it a zm map. Map name is zm_zombie_slider_a1.bsp. You can download the latest version here. I will be updating it frequently until completion. As of now, all of the obstacles lead back to the start. My end game is going to be a large arena where the level of difficulty of the obstacle takes you to better spots. Enjoy!
